### ğŸ”¥ Real-life Example:

Tu apne ghar ka **WiFi router** update karta hai, par soch ki update hone ke baad bhi **internet band na ho**.
Bas wahi **Rolling Update** ka concept hai.

### âœ”ï¸ Definition:

Rolling Update means **application ko new version me update karna, bina downtime ke**.

### âœ”ï¸ Kubernetes me kaise hota hai?

Kubernetes tumhare deployment ke pods ko:

1. **Ek-ek karke** purane pods ko delete karta hai
2. Phir **ek-ek karke** naye version ke pods create karta hai
